      <title>中国库存不断增加，铁矿石困境加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/iron-ore-woes-deepen-as-inventories-in-china-keep-piling-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石暴跌5%——并短暂跌破每吨110美元大关——由于中国的需求令人失望，导致市场库存膨胀。]]></description>
